{{Top|ncl}}
{{Unlicensed}}[[NavStar Transport]] was a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] front company, which was once used to get a group of rebels on board the ''[[Arion Star]]'' from [[Tancon]] to [[Greyman's Planet]] so that they could meet with [[Roger Stern]] of [[Stern Traders]]. There, they used the company name to gain supplies from him to transport to [[Karinda Outpost]].

